ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of OMAR FAROUK of Brampton, Ontario, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Immigration at Pier 21, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective July 1, 2019, in the place of Carrie Ross, whose term has expired.
